OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FA justice minister has agreed to meet
OL,8,Fa bereaved mother from the Wirral who
OL,9,Fis calling for a change in the law for
OL,10,Fmurderers who conceal their victim's
OL,11,Fbody.
OL,13,FJean Taylor's daughter Chantel was
OL,14,Fkilled by Stephen Wynne, then aged 26,
OL,15,Fwhen he attacked the mother-of-three
OL,16,Fwith a meat cleaver after meeting near
OL,17,Fhis home in Birkenhead, Merseyside, in
OL,18,FMarch 2004.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
