OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FWynne admitted to murdering the 27-
OL,8,Fyear-old and was jailed for life at
OL,9,FLiverpool Crown Court in January 2006.
OL,11,FHis sentence was later reduced on
OL,12,Fappeal to 18 years and he was granted
OL,13,Fparole earlier this year.
OL,15,FJean Taylor is now campaigning for
OL,16,FChantel's law which would make
OL,17,Fconcealment or desecration of a body a
OL,18,F"crime in its own right", Conservative
OL,19,Fformer minister Esther McVey told the
OL,20,FCommons.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FThere is not currently an explicit
OL,8,Foffence of desecration of a dead body
OL,9,Fin England and Wales.
OL,11,FJustice minister Alex Davies-Jones
OL,12,Fsaid this is being looked at by the
OL,13,FLaw Commission.
OL,15,FAt women and equalities questions on
OL,16,FWednesday, Ms McVey, MP for Tatton,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Jean Taylor set up the
OL,18,Forganisation Families Fighting for
OL,19,FJustice after her daughter Chantel
OL,20,FTaylor was violently and savagely
OL,21,Fmurdered.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,F"The murderer then desecrated and
OL,8,Fconcealed her body, and Jean Taylor is
OL,9,Fwanting to make sure that this is a
OL,10,Fcrime in its own right and not just an
OL,11,Faggravating factor.
OL,13,F"Because not only could she not grieve
OL,14,Fher daughter or bury her daughter, and
OL,15,FChantel's three children couldn't
OL,16,Feither, but in hiding the body serious
OL,17,Fevidence also was hidden.
OL,19,F"The murderer is now out on the
OL,20,Fstreets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,F"Please, will the minister meet with
OL,8,Fme and Jean Taylor to discuss a
OL,9,FChantel's law?"
OL,11,FMs Davies-Jones replied: "I will
OL,12,Fcommit today to meeting with her and
OL,13,FJean to discuss this.
OL,15,F"She will know that the Law Commission
OL,16,Fare looking at specifically
OL,17,Fdesecration of a body, and that work
OL,18,Fis ongoing, and that we as a
OL,19,FGovernment, when they report back,
OL,20,Fwill look at that carefully to see
OL,21,Fwhat more we can do.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@OO]sD@ZOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,F"But I do know that this is an issue,
OL,8,Fand I will happily meet with her and
OL,9,FJean."
OL,11,FElsewhere in the session, Equalities
OL,12,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson said she
OL,13,Fis "fed up to the back teeth of
OL,14,Fopposition politicians coming here
OL,15,Ftime and time again to sow division
OL,16,Facross our country".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@FO]uD@DOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
