PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777539988
OL,3,CGrieving mum to meet minister over
OL,4,Ccampaign to change desecration of body
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,FThis came in response to shadow
OL,8,Fequalities minister Claire Coutinho
OL,9,Fwho said: "The Muslim Vote campaign is
OL,10,Ftelling people how to vote depending
OL,11,Fon what God they pray to.
OL,13,F"This is divisive, sectarian, and it
OL,14,Fhas no place in Britain."
OL,26,@qD@KOUuD@AOUvD@YO]
